Realm Chapter - Furry Infestation

On a morning in Nisreenanus, Nisreen woke up to news from her servant of an infestation of furries dressed as rabbits threatening the kingdom's people, and she responded:

​

"I'll take down those furry mkhanatheen!"
"WHO'S WITH ME, BITCHES?"

​

"I SERVE MA QUEEN, WE FINNA SLAY THEM FURRIES!!" said her servant, Black Ruba.

​

After getting ready and dressed up to slay, Nisreen went on to recruit more people to fight the furries alongside her. She recruited her son Mashhour, and Sima - who responded, "A chance to fight FURRIES?! SIGN ME UP."

​

After a few hours, the group assembled in Berwaz Forest near the Behind the Sun Kingdom to fight the furries!

​

"YALA TOLAB! LET'S SHOW THOSE FURRIES THAT NISREENANUS ISN'T FOR LE-MKHANATHEEN!" shouted Nisreen.

​

The fight was slow and painstaking work. Queen Nisreen and her group had to move slowly through the forest to avoid startling the horny furry rabbits who were having sex before they could launch their attack. Although they did slay a few of the horny furries, the majority were able to flee... 

​

"Who knew furries could have such rough sex? Well *in a southern accent 💅*, we didn't get them all, but we made sure the ones who survived will be telling their descendants about us, unless we find a better way to get rid of them all. We should discuss this further!" said Nisreen.

​

When the group returned to the castle to figure out another plan, Sima remembered reading rumors about a curse book called "The DarkKoss" that contained a specific curse that could help with the situation.

​

"You know what- It may sound crazy, but I once read a book about a curse that can be cast on living things to make them go crazy and kill themselves!" said Sima.

​

Everyone seemed to be on board with the plan, but the problem was that they had to find the book, which is rumored to be hidden in a cave on Planet Fayrouzto, and in that cave lies a creature, a fairy with four eyes, called Ka7bababy.

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

​

​

​

​

​

The group didn't have any other ideas, so Nisreen agreed to go with Sima only on this dangerous mission to see if the rumors were true and to find the book. As soon as Nisreen and Sima arrived on Planet Fayrouzto, they began looking for the cave. The cave was difficult to find, but with the help of Nisreen's powers, they were able to locate it!

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

As soon as they entered the cave, it was dark and gloomy, and the creature attacked them and teleported them to a void where it continued its attack. Nisreen and Sima had to fight, but in the end, thanks to Nisreen's godly powers and Sima's powerful magic, they were able to defeat Ka7bababy, but both of them were still trapped inside the void the creature had placed them in, and neither Nisreen's nor Sima's teleportation powers could help. Sima then cast a Revealio spell, revealing a light that they followed until they reached an altar that had The DarkKoss, and as soon as they grabbed the book, they were teleported out of the void and were once again able to use their powers to return to Nisreenanus!

​

Back in the forest near the Behind the Sun Kingdom, Sima began preparing the curse, adding her own touch to it by making the spell transform the furries dressed as rabbits into actual rabbits, making them more helpless when they get cursed. The text in the book went on to say, "As soon as the curse is unleashed in the area, the caster shall flee lest they get cursed too." The curse was unleashed, Nisreen and Sima fled, and the curse worked!

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

The furries transformed into rabbits, and they began killing themselves. And even if some of them didn't get cursed, their offspring would be born with the curse and would eventually kill themselves, leading the furries to fatal extinction! After that, the group and the people of Nisreenanus drank to celebrate their victory against the horny furries!
